root: ^Well done! Please return to the moon pool, a drone is waiting to take you to the surface.
^I shall self-destruct the station in 5 minutes.
^[you return to the moon pool and get picked up by a company drone]
^Reports state that SEA.E.O’s underwater station has unexpectedly exploded.
^An investigation is under way, but too much of the station is missing to determine much.
^In other news, SEA.E.O employee 357 and 401 are still missing.
